2006-02-06  Michal Konieczny  <mk@m.mfk.net.pl>

	* src/bdm12pod.c:
	* src/bdm12pod.h:
	fixed serial port handshake timing

	* src/hc12mcu.c: fix read of FPROT register (previously it was read
	directly from memory, now is properly accessed via registers)
	fixed FPROT bits interpretation for some patterns
	increased s-record data gap size to 4 bytes for skipping when sending
	data to be programmed into FLASH

	* src/srec.c: add default mode for no address translation when passed
	translation routine address = NULL

